data.description: Hey there, house hunters! Nestled in west Greeley, this isn't just a home-it's a haven with endless possibilities. 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a 2-car garage await you.Tucked in the quiet, desirable Pheasant Run neighborhood, there's NO HOA or pesky Metro Tax, & this gem is move-in ready. Built in 1978 and renovated in 2018, it's bursting with flair-LVP flooring, sleek granite counters, and four skylights for that bright and cheerful vibe.Need space for your busy lifestyle? We've got you covered. Two primary bedrooms with ensuite bathrooms and generous closets offer comfort and convenience, whether you're hosting friends, working from home, or embracing multi-generational living.Let's talk kitchen dreams. Granite counters, ample cabinet space, a pantry, and a roomy breakfast bar for socializing while you cook up a storm!Venture downstairs to find a second primary suite with its own 3/4 bath-perfect for guests or a peaceful retreat. Two additional bedrooms, a spacious great room, and plenty of storage options ensure every inch of this home is utilized.Step outside to your private hideaway. The fenced yard features a patio, RV/boat parking, and a charming pergola for those breezy afternoons. Embrace your inner gardener with raised flower beds and mature trees.You'll be worry-free with the Radon mitigation system and a whole-house fan to keep things fresh and safe. Bonus: the seller will provide a 1-year Home Warranty too. Ready to turn this house into your dream home? Check it out today!
